               <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_863"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__thomas_swaeml_QGW_II_I_1012">Thoman der Swemmbel, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien-buergerspital">obrister spitalmaister</roleName> der
